                    portal allows students to register, choose subjects, and track academic progress, while empowering
                    department-level admins to float subjects, review applications, and manage student data efficiently.</p>
                <p> This platform aims to eliminate manual paperwork and reduce communication gaps between departments and
                    students, making academic processes smoother, faster, and fully digital.</p>
            </div>
            
        </section>
